metadata.description:
The pastel colours used in the piece add to the sense of peacefulness and harmony, but the bleeding of the colours within the face creates a sense of unease and instability. It's as if the face is trying to hold onto the beauty of nature, but it is being consumed by the imbalance that currently exists.

The strong, determined lines of the face show a resilience and determination to overcome these challenges and restore balance. It is a powerful reminder of the interconnectedness of all things, and the importance of respecting and protecting the natural world.
metadata.title: Interconnectedness #1 of 9
metadata.subtitle: Hope and Resilience
metadata.name: Interconnectedness #1 of 9
